156
00:16:32,779 --> 00:16:37,139
[SPEAKER_00] Kao da njegovo izdavanje postane samo sebi svrha.

157
00:16:37,139 --> 00:16:39,200
[SPEAKER_00] Sad u tom kontekstu, mene zanima,

158
00:16:39,200 --> 00:16:41,220
[SPEAKER_00] može li neki vjernik,

159
00:16:41,220 --> 00:16:45,019
[SPEAKER_00] a vjernici, to ćete i kasnije moći sami reći,

160
00:16:45,019 --> 00:16:47,440
[SPEAKER_00] dostupan ovaj sadržaj i online,

161
00:16:47,440 --> 00:16:49,980
[SPEAKER_00] može li neki vjernik u nekoj župi

162
00:16:49,980 --> 00:16:52,139
[SPEAKER_00] Zagrebačke na bliskupije uzeti ovu knjigu

163
00:16:52,139 --> 00:16:53,799
[SPEAKER_00] za interesiranoju, početi čitati

164
00:16:53,799 --> 00:16:57,679
[SPEAKER_00] i onda unutra nađe neku zgodnu preporuku.

165
00:16:57,820 --> 00:16:58,340
[SPEAKER_00] Konkretnu.

166
00:16:58,340 --> 00:17:00,220
[SPEAKER_00] Unutra ima, inače moram vam reći,

167
00:17:00,220 --> 00:17:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] cijenjeni gledatelji i slušatelji,

168
00:17:02,000 --> 00:17:03,340
