169
00:17:03,340 --> 00:17:06,420
[SPEAKER_00] o kojima je možda i netko od vas

170
00:17:06,420 --> 00:17:07,819
[SPEAKER_00] na trenutki razmišljao,

171
00:17:07,819 --> 00:17:10,319
[SPEAKER_00] ali nije ih nikad izrekao

172
00:17:10,319 --> 00:17:12,099
