173
00:17:12,099 --> 00:17:15,740
[SPEAKER_00] Padaju mi na pamet neke konkretne prijedloze.

174
00:17:15,740 --> 00:17:18,539
[SPEAKER_00] Recimo, da se unutar njihove župe

175
00:17:18,539 --> 00:17:20,359
[SPEAKER_00] ustanovi biblijska skupina,

176
00:17:20,359 --> 00:17:24,380
[SPEAKER_00] jer bi on rado nečemu takvom usudjelovao,

177
00:17:24,380 --> 00:17:25,720
[SPEAKER_00] čita doma sam Bibliju,

178
00:17:25,720 --> 00:17:29,119
[SPEAKER_00] rado bi da to može podijeliti s nekim drugim,

179
00:17:29,119 --> 00:17:31,900
[SPEAKER_00] da mu netko, neki poznavatelj Biblije

180
00:17:31,900 --> 00:17:35,740
[SPEAKER_00] jedan put mjesečno ili u nekoj drugom dinamikom

181
00:17:35,740 --> 00:17:37,140
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi u župu

182
00:17:37,140 --> 00:17:40,559
[SPEAKER_00] i da vjernici raspravljaju o biblijskim sadržajima.

183
00:17:40,559 --> 00:17:42,339
[SPEAKER_00] Ili ne znam, još konkretnije,

184
00:17:42,339 --> 00:17:43,819
[SPEAKER_00] vidi pred crkvom,

185
00:17:43,819 --> 00:17:47,940
[SPEAKER_00] ima mjesta gdje bi se mogla napraviti rampa za invalide,

186
00:17:47,940 --> 00:17:49,759
[SPEAKER_00] a on ima invalidnog, dakle,

187
00:17:49,759 --> 00:17:54,220
[SPEAKER_00] ukućanina sa poteškoćama u kretanju.

188
00:17:54,220 --> 00:17:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Može li on doći svom župniku

189
00:17:56,000 --> 00:17:57,180
