[SPEAKER_00] trebali shvatiti kao jednu ipak smjerokaz

207
00:18:39,019 --> 00:18:41,859
[SPEAKER_00] u svom budućem upravljanju

208
00:18:41,859 --> 00:18:43,400
[SPEAKER_00] i pastoralnom djelovanju?

209
00:18:43,400 --> 00:18:46,140
[SPEAKER_01] Izjave i odluke druge sinode

210
00:18:46,140 --> 00:18:47,440
[SPEAKER_01] Zagrebačke nadiskupije

211
00:18:47,440 --> 00:18:48,960
[SPEAKER_01] su partikularno pravo

