[SPEAKER_01] tako izjave i odluke druge sinode

219
00:19:08,559 --> 00:19:09,940
[SPEAKER_01] Zagrebačke nadiskupije

220
00:19:09,940 --> 00:19:12,680
[SPEAKER_01] su partikularno krajevno pravo

221
00:19:12,680 --> 00:19:15,420
[SPEAKER_01] koje obvezuje vjernike

222
00:19:15,420 --> 00:19:16,799
[SPEAKER_01] Zagrebačke nadiskupije.

223
00:19:16,799 --> 00:19:18,460
[SPEAKER_01] I tu je stvar jasna.

224
00:19:19,420 --> 00:19:21,440
[SPEAKER_01] Kad vi kažete, evo ga,

225
00:19:21,440 --> 00:19:23,740
[SPEAKER_01] tražiti, zahtijevati,

226
00:19:23,740 --> 00:19:25,460
