227
00:19:25,460 --> 00:19:28,259
[SPEAKER_00] Može to biti i moliti.

228
00:19:28,259 --> 00:19:29,980
[SPEAKER_01] Evo ga, onda taj glagol

229
00:19:29,980 --> 00:19:32,160
[SPEAKER_01] tražiti, zahtijevati,

230
00:19:32,160 --> 00:19:35,599
[SPEAKER_01] pa čak i nekako mi ne ide,

231
00:19:35,599 --> 00:19:38,259
