[SPEAKER_01] zahtijevati kao da to treba

237
00:19:50,599 --> 00:19:52,180
[SPEAKER_01] netko drugi,

238
00:19:52,180 --> 00:19:55,180
[SPEAKER_01] a ja tu ne moram ništa.

239
00:19:55,180 --> 00:19:58,059
[SPEAKER_01] Nego ja bih bio više za to

240
