247
00:20:13,160 --> 00:20:14,279
[SPEAKER_01] da u našoj

248
00:20:14,279 --> 00:20:15,960
[SPEAKER_01] Zagrebačkoj nadiskupije,

249
00:20:15,960 --> 00:20:17,519
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno u našoj župi

250
00:20:17,519 --> 00:20:19,079
[SPEAKER_01] Zagrebačke nadiskupije,

251
00:20:19,079 --> 00:20:21,420
[SPEAKER_01] postoji biblijska skupina

252
