[SPEAKER_01] dajem na raspolaganje.

256
00:20:28,259 --> 00:20:30,220
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam to pročitao.

257
00:20:30,220 --> 00:20:32,599
[SPEAKER_01] Želim zajedno s vama

258
00:20:32,599 --> 00:20:33,759
[SPEAKER_01] pomoći vam

259
00:20:33,759 --> 00:20:34,799
[SPEAKER_01] da mi oformimo

260
