288
00:21:13,400 --> 00:21:15,039
[SPEAKER_01] to nije novotarija,

289
00:21:15,039 --> 00:21:16,700
[SPEAKER_01] nijedan župnik,

290
00:21:16,700 --> 00:21:17,559
[SPEAKER_01] nijedan župnik

291
00:21:17,559 --> 00:21:18,420
